<figureCitation box="[378,505,1689,1715]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1372,1396]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,489,1346]" captionTargetId="figure-181@2.[151,1435,489,1349]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Rovnodryinus khomychi, ♀ holotype. A, latero-ventral view; B, latero-dorsal view; C, head and pronotum in laterodorsal view; D, head and propleuron in ventral view. oc = ocellus. Scale bar: 2.3 mm for A, 2.1 mm for B, 0.5 mm for C, 0.6 mm for D." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6796775" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6796775/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="56">Figs 1A, B</figureCitation>
